exceptions.exn: In environment E, E' : Ens H : IN E' (Power E) The term "H" has type "IN E' (Power E)" while it is expected to have type "EQ ?E' ?E''".
In environment E, E' : Ens H : IN E' (Power E) The term "Sing E'" has type "Ens" while it is expected to have type "EQ ?E ?E'".
In environment E, E' : Ens H : IN E' (Power E) Unable to unify "IN E' (Sing E')" with "INC E' E".

original: intros E E' H. apply (INC_sound_right _ _ _ H). apply (IN_sound_left _ _ _ (Sing E')). apply (IN_Sing E').
